    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#1B2A4A] mt-8 mb-4">12.1 Delivery Model</h3>

    <p class="mb-4 text-[#2D2D2D] leading-relaxed">
      <strong>Two senior developers, 4.5 combined days per week, eight weeks.</strong> Development is AI-augmented &mdash; BrightKeep uses production-grade AI coding tools that accelerate implementation while maintaining code quality through continuous human oversight and review.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-4 text-[#2D2D2D] leading-relaxed">
      <strong>Capacity:</strong> 3 days/week (Delivery Lead) + 1.5 days/week (Technical Lead) = 4.5 person-days/week.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-4 text-[#2D2D2D] leading-relaxed">
      <strong>Why this works for this project:</strong>
    </p>

    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2 text-[#2D2D2D]">
      <li>Cloud9 has a working prototype with real client data, so discovery is confirmation, not exploration</li>
      <li>The tech stack is well-established and well-documented</li>
      <li>Single-tenant deployment is architecturally simpler than multi-tenant</li>
      <li>The modular monolith architecture allows both developers to work in parallel</li>
      <li>AI-augmented development handles the bulk of implementation work</li>
    </ul>

