            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2">Comprehensive list of everything needed to build, provided to Cloud9&rsquo;s BA</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50">
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2">SharePoint schema confirmation</td>
            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2">Validate column mapping against the working prototype&rsquo;s data</td>
