            <td class="border border-gray-200 px-3 py-2">Single-tenant approach, URL pattern, auth model confirmed</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <p class="mb-4 text-[#2D2D2D] leading-relaxed">
      Discovery runs in parallel with Cloud9&rsquo;s internal processes. BrightKeep provides the requirements template on day one; Cloud9&rsquo;s BA populates it with input from Veronica and the consulting team. The key prerequisite is SharePoint access &mdash; BrightKeep needs read access to the pilot client&rsquo;s SharePoint lists to validate the data model. The gate for Phase 1 is confirmed SharePoint schema and an Entra app registration in progress.
    </p>

